        <h3>5. Advertising Disclaimer</h3>
        <p>This website may be considered <strong>Attorney Advertising</strong> under the rules of the Kentucky Bar Association.</p>

        <h3>6. Copyright</h3>
        <p>Content on this website, including the "EH" logo, design, text, and original photography, is &copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} Ebert Haegele. All rights reserved.</p>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer slot="footer" />
</MainLayout>
